subsection.content:
providing items
                    in the possession of the authorities of the requested
                    Party;

presenting an invitation to a person whose
                    appearance before an appropriate authority in the requesting Party is
                    sought;

transfer of a person in custody for giving
                    testimony or otherwise assisting in investigations, prosecutions or other
                    proceedings;

assisting in proceedings related to confiscation
                    and immobilization of proceeds or instrumentalities of criminal offences;
                    and

the name of the authority conducting the
                    investigation, prosecution or other
                    proceeding;

information on the identity and whereabouts of any
                    person from whom testimony, statements or items are
                    sought;

a description of the manner in which testimony,
                    statements or items are to be obtained or
                    recorded;

a list of questions to be asked of the person from
                    whom testimony, statements or items are
                    sought;

information on the identity and location of a
                    person to be served, that person’s relationship to the proceedings, and the
                    manner in which service is to be made;

information on the allowances and expenses to which
                    a person whose appearance is sought before the appropriate authority in the
                    requesting Party will be entitled;
